---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import AuditForm from '../../components/AuditForm.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="About — Eddie Miller Agency"
  description="Eddie Miller Agency helps local businesses be found by their future customers on Google and AI. Discover our team and approach."
  canonicalUrl="https://eddiemiller.agency/en/about"
  ogTitle="About — Eddie Miller Agency"
  ogDescription="The team that helps local businesses be found by their future customers."
>
  <Header />

  <main id="main-content" class="pt-28 md:pt-32">

    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="py-16 md:py-24 lg:py-32 bg-cream" aria-label="Who we are">
      <div class="max-w-container mx-auto px-6 md:px-8 lg:px-16">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
          <h1 class="text-[2.5rem] md:text-[3.25rem] lg:text-[4rem] font-serif font-normal leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.02em] text-charcoal fade-up-slow">
            The team behind your visibility
          </h1>
          <div class="mx-auto mt-6 separator-animate h-[2px] bg-terracotta" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <p class="mt-6 md:mt-8 text-lg md:text-xl font-sans font-normal leading-relaxed text-stone fade-up">
            We are a team of local visibility specialists. Our job: making sure your future customers find you on Google, Google Maps, and AI assistants like ChatGPT.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Our mission -->
    <section class="py-16 md:py-24 lg:py-32 bg-sand" aria-label="Our mission">
      <div class="max-w-container mx-auto px-6 md:px-8 lg:px-16">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-[2rem] md:text-[3rem] font-serif font-normal leading-[1.15] tracking-[-0.02em] text-charcoal mb-4 fade-up-slow">
            Our mission
          </h2>
          <div class="mx-auto mb-8 separator-animate h-[2px] bg-terracotta" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="space-y-6 fade-up">
            <p class="text-base md:text-lg font-sans font-normal leading-relaxed text-stone">
              Every day, thousands of people ask Google or ChatGPT to recommend a dentist, a restaurant, a lawyer, or a hair salon near them. The results they get are not random: they depend on specific signals that most professionals don't control.
            </p>
            <p class="text-base md:text-lg font-sans font-normal leading-relaxed text-stone">
              Our mission is simple: make sure the best professionals are also the most visible. Not the ones with the biggest marketing budget, but the ones who deserve to be found by their future customers.
            </p>
            <p class="text-base md:text-lg font-sans font-normal leading-relaxed text-stone">
              We have supported dozens of local businesses (dental practices, restaurants, hotels, law firms, hair salons, spas, and gyms) with a proven method and measurable results.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Founder -->
    <section class="py-16 md:py-24 lg:py-32 bg-cream" aria-label="The founder">
      <div class="max-w-container mx-auto px-6 md:px-8 lg:px-16">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-[2rem] md:text-[3rem] font-serif font-normal leading-[1.15] tracking-[-0.02em] text-charcoal mb-4 fade-up-slow">
            Who is behind Eddie Miller Agency
          </h2>
          <div class="mx-auto mb-8 separator-animate h-[2px] bg-terracotta" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="space-y-6 fade-up">
            <p class="text-base md:text-lg font-sans font-normal leading-relaxed text-stone">
              My name is <strong class="text-charcoal">Adam</strong>. Before creating Eddie Miller Agency, I spent years understanding how Google decides who to show first, and how AI assistants like ChatGPT choose which professionals to recommend.
            </p>
            <p class="text-base md:text-lg font-sans font-normal leading-relaxed text-stone">
              I noticed a simple problem: the best professionals — those with the best reviews, the best service — are often the least visible online. Not because they're bad, but because nobody showed them how these new channels work.
            </p>
            <p class="text-base md:text-lg font-sans font-normal leading-relaxed text-stone">
              That's why I created this agency. My goal is concrete: when someone in your area asks ChatGPT or searches Google for a professional in your field, it's your name that comes up.
            </p>
            <p class="text-base md:text-lg font-sans font-normal leading-relaxed text-stone">
              I personally work on every diagnostic and every engagement. It's me who will call you after your diagnostic. Not an intern, not a salesperson — the person who will actually work on your visibility.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- What we do -->
    <section class="py-16 md:py-24 lg:py-32 bg-sand" aria-label="Our expertise">
      <div class="max-w-container mx-auto px-6 md:px-8 lg:px-16">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-[2rem] md:text-[3rem] font-serif font-normal leading-[1.15] tracking-[-0.02em] text-charcoal mb-4 fade-up-slow">
            Our expertise
          </h2>
          <div class="mx-auto mb-8 separator-animate h-[2px] bg-terracotta" aria-hidden="true"></div>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 md:gap-8 fade-up">
            <div class="border border-warmgray p-8 bg-cream card-hover">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-terracotta" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
                  <circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><path d="m21 21-4.35-4.35"/>
                </svg>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-serif font-normal text-charcoal">Google and Google Maps</h3>
              </div>
              <p class="text-base font-sans font-normal leading-relaxed text-stone">
                Optimized Google Business profiles, review strategy, local visibility: we master every lever that places you ahead of your competitors on Google Maps and in search results.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="border border-warmgray p-8 bg-cream card-hover">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-terracotta" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path d="M12 3c.5 3.5 2 5 5.5 5.5-3.5.5-5 2-5.5 5.5-.5-3.5-2-5-5.5-5.5C10 8 11.5 6.5 12 3Z"/>
                  <path d="M19 10c.3 2 1.2 3 3.3 3.3-2.1.3-3 1.2-3.3 3.3-.3-2.1-1.2-3-3.3-3.3 2.1-.3 3-1.3 3.3-3.3Z"/>
                </svg>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-serif font-normal text-charcoal">AI assistants</h3>
              </div>
              <p class="text-base font-sans font-normal leading-relaxed text-stone">
                ChatGPT, Gemini, Perplexity: these tools now recommend local professionals to millions of users. Our team knows exactly which signals to activate so your business gets mentioned.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="border border-warmgray p-8 bg-cream card-hover">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-terracotta" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path d="M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2"/>
                </svg>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-serif font-normal text-charcoal">Measurement and results</h3>
              </div>
              <p class="text-base font-sans font-normal leading-relaxed text-stone">
                Every action is measured. We use a visibility score across 100 real queries to quantify your progress. No vague promises, just concrete numbers.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="border border-warmgray p-8 bg-cream card-hover">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-terracotta" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/>
                  <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/>
                  <path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/>
                  <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/>
                </svg>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-serif font-normal text-charcoal">Geographic exclusivity</h3>
              </div>
              <p class="text-base font-sans font-normal leading-relaxed text-stone">
                We only work with one client per neighborhood and specialty. That is our guarantee: your success will never compete with another one of our clients.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Why us -->
    <section class="py-16 md:py-24 lg:py-32 bg-sand" aria-label="Why Eddie Miller Agency">
      <div class="max-w-container mx-auto px-6 md:px-8 lg:px-16">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-[2rem] md:text-[3rem] font-serif font-normal leading-[1.15] tracking-[-0.02em] text-charcoal mb-4 fade-up-slow">
            Why trust us
          </h2>
          <div class="mx-auto mb-8 separator-animate h-[2px] bg-terracotta" aria-hidden="true"></div>

          <div class="space-y-8 fade-up">
            <div class="flex gap-6 items-start">
              <p class="text-[3rem] font-serif font-normal leading-none text-warmgray/25 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">01</p>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-normal leading-[1.2] text-charcoal mb-2">Specialists, not generalists</h3>
                <p class="text-base font-sans font-normal leading-relaxed text-stone">
                  We don't build websites, run ads, or manage social media. Our only job: making your business visible where your future customers are searching. This specialization makes us more effective than any generalist agency.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex gap-6 items-start">
              <p class="text-[3rem] font-serif font-normal leading-none text-warmgray/25 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">02</p>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-normal leading-[1.2] text-charcoal mb-2">Results, not reports</h3>
                <p class="text-base font-sans font-normal leading-relaxed text-stone">
                  Our clients measure impact in new patients, covers served, or bookings, not in pages of PowerPoint. Every action we take is designed for a concrete impact on your business.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex gap-6 items-start">
              <p class="text-[3rem] font-serif font-normal leading-none text-warmgray/25 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">03</p>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-normal leading-[1.2] text-charcoal mb-2">A proven method</h3>
                <p class="text-base font-sans font-normal leading-relaxed text-stone">
                  Our methodology combines traditional Google optimization with the latest techniques for AI visibility. We test, measure, and adjust continuously, because algorithms evolve, and so do we.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex gap-6 items-start">
              <p class="text-[3rem] font-serif font-normal leading-none text-warmgray/25 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">04</p>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-normal leading-[1.2] text-charcoal mb-2">Complete transparency</h3>
                <p class="text-base font-sans font-normal leading-relaxed text-stone">
                  No technical jargon, no hidden contracts, no inflated results. You know exactly what we do, why we do it, and what impact it has. The free diagnostic is our way of proving it before you commit.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>

  <AuditForm />
  <Footer />
</Layout>
